oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Crazy Water Crystals Program #10
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Crazy Water Crystals program #10, sponsored by the Crazy Water Crystal company. Hosted by Bill Karn (name unconfirmed), with the Crazy Radio Gang, the Milo Twins, the Boys In Buckskin (including Elmer and Jake), Martha Jordan (real name Dorothy Martha), Ritchie, Sammy, Doc, and Julian.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Crazy Radio Gang; Martha Jordan; Milo Twins; Boys In Buckskin
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Theme -- Opening statement (Bill Karn) -- Soldier's Joy (Ritchie fiddle) -- Crazy Water Crystals commercial (Bill Karn) -- Bill Karn introduces the Boys In Buckskin -- Oh My Darling, Clementine (Boys In Buckskin) -- Crazy Water Crystals commercial (Bill Karn) -- Bill Karn and Sammy talk -- Bill Karn introduces Martha Jordan -- Going Back To Texas (Martha Jordan) -- Bill Karn introduces the Milo Twins -- I've Got The Railroad Blues (Milo Twins) -- Crazy Water Crystals offer (Bill Karn) -- Bill Karn introduces Julian -- Dream Train (Julian guitar, Doc guitar) -- Closing statement (Bill Karn) -- Theme
